org.apache.xpath.types

Class XMLAttribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.xpath.Expression
      • org.apache.xpath.objects.XObject
        • org.apache.xpath.types.XMLAttribute
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.xml.transform.SourceLocator, ExpressionNode, XPathVisitable

    public class XMLAttribute
extends XObject
    A class representing an XML attribute's name components and value. The main use for this class is, when an xsl:function constructs only an attribute node via xsl:attribute instruction.
